  "detailed_description": "Jump back to the good old days of arcade machines with <strong>Void Invaders</strong>: a colourful, chaotic and explosive arcade shoot-em-up game inspired by classics such as Galaga and Space Invaders! Blast your way through more than 40 levels filled with dozens of enemies, intense boss fights and destructive powerups! Explosive visuals and a frantic light show included.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Colourful and explosive retro graphics!<br></li><li>Over 40 levels to beat!<br></li><li>More than 70 different enemies!<br></li><li>Insane boss battles!<br></li><li>Multiple challenging game modes!<br></li><li>Full controller support!<br></li><li>Achievements!<br></li><li>Online leaderboards!</li></ul><br>",
